Oh well.  AE was fun while it lasted.  It made a good change of pace when you got tired of the standard group form.  If a bunch of greenies jump you, you don't need an upgrade to scin.  Sure, a new one might be a bit more efficient or give you a good second AE to cast while waiting on scin, but there are many greens I simply can't AE more than four or five of at a time due to my HP/AC (neither is great, but I would assume they are average).  It is easier to just keep running if in an outdoor zone and run 3 is more than enough to put a good bit of distance between you and many mobs.<br>
<br>
